<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1950,2012]" lastBlockId="6.[151,1437,151,824]" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="557" pageId="5" pageNumber="556">
<bibRefCitation author="Gaedike" box="[199,375,1950,1975]" pageId="5" pageNumber="556" refString="Gaedike, H. (1971) Katalog der in den Sammlungen des ehemaligen Deutschen Entomologischen Institutes aufbewahrten Typen. - V. Beitrage zur Entomologie, 21 (1 - 2), 79 - 159." type="journal article" year="1971">
Gaedike (
<number box="[310,368,1951,1975]" pageId="5" pageNumber="556" value="1971.0">1971</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
fixed the identity of 
<taxonomicName box="[621,740,1951,1975]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="84" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="556" phylum="Arthropoda" species="fenestra">
<emphasis box="[621,740,1951,1975]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="556">P. fenestra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by designating a specimen from Marcapata as the 
<typeStatus box="[1327,1432,1950,1975]" pageId="5" pageNumber="556">lectotype</typeStatus>
, and listed a 
<typeStatus box="[301,452,1987,2012]" pageId="5" pageNumber="556">paralectotype</typeStatus>
from Amazonas and two 
<typeStatus box="[767,929,1987,2012]" pageId="5" pageNumber="556">paralectotypes</typeStatus>
from Huancabamba, all 
<collectingCountry box="[1226,1281,1988,2011]" name="Peru" pageId="5" pageNumber="556">Peru</collectingCountry>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Eger" box="[1297,1436,1987,2012]" pageId="5" pageNumber="556" refString="Eger, J. E. Jr. (1990) Revision of the genus Polytes Stal (Heteroptera: Scutelleridae). Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 83 (2), 115 - 141. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / 83.2.115" type="journal article" year="1990">
Eger (
<number box="[1370,1428,1987,2011]" pageId="5" pageNumber="556" value="1990.0">1990</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
pointed out that neither of the 
<typeStatus box="[508,670,151,176]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">paralectotypes</typeStatus>
is conspecific with the 
<typeStatus box="[951,1056,151,176]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">lectotype</typeStatus>
, and he designated the one from Amazonas as a 
<typeStatus box="[329,426,189,213]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">paratype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[466,599,188,212]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="194" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="quechuus">
<emphasis box="[466,599,188,212]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. quechuus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<bibRefCitation author="Eger" box="[608,735,188,213]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" refString="Eger, J. E. Jr. (1990) Revision of the genus Polytes Stal (Heteroptera: Scutelleridae). Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 83 (2), 115 - 141. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / 83.2.115" type="journal article" year="1990">
Eger, 
<number box="[675,735,188,212]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" value="1990.0">1990</number>
</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Eger" box="[747,882,188,213]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" refString="Eger, J. E. Jr. (1990) Revision of the genus Polytes Stal (Heteroptera: Scutelleridae). Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 83 (2), 115 - 141. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / 83.2.115" type="journal article" year="1990">
Eger (
<number box="[816,874,188,212]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" value="1990.0">1990</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
also claimed that the latter specimen contradicts the original description therefore it is probably not part of the original 
<typeStatus box="[944,992,224,248]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">type</typeStatus>
series of 
<emphasis box="[1102,1217,224,248]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">
<taxonomicName box="[1102,1184,224,248]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="173" genus.bestMatchVote="1" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="fenes">P. fenes</taxonomicName>
tra
</emphasis>
. Later 
<bibRefCitation author="Eger" box="[1300,1436,224,248]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" refString="Eger, J. E. Jr. (1994) New synonymy in the genus Polytes Stal (Heteroptera, Scutelleridae). Florida Entomologist, 77 (3), 376 - 378. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.2307 / 3496108" type="journal article" year="1994">
Eger (
<number box="[1369,1428,224,248]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" value="1994.0">1994</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
recognized 
<taxonomicName box="[281,414,260,284]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="238" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="quechuus">
<emphasis box="[281,414,260,284]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. quechuus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a junior subjective synonym of 
<taxonomicName box="[805,948,260,284]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="249" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="speculiger">
<emphasis box="[805,948,260,284]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. speculiger</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,151,824]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">
The 
<typeStatus box="[252,300,296,320]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">type</typeStatus>
material of 
<taxonomicName box="[443,589,296,320]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="241" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="speculiger">
<emphasis box="[443,589,296,320]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. speculiger</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has remained unlocated so far. A thorough search in Breddin’s collection deposited in 
<collectionCode box="[294,356,332,356]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">SDEI</collectionCode>
revealed a male from the 
<typeStatus box="[648,696,333,357]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">type</typeStatus>
locality of 
<emphasis box="[824,964,332,356]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. s p ec u l i ge r</emphasis>
, bearing no identification label but fitting the description of “var. a” of 
<emphasis box="[476,616,368,392]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. s p ec u l i ge r</emphasis>
; the specimen is selected as 
<typeStatus box="[941,1044,367,392]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">lectotype</typeStatus>
of this species. This specimen was not listed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Gaedike" box="[300,476,404,429]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" refString="Gaedike, H. (1971) Katalog der in den Sammlungen des ehemaligen Deutschen Entomologischen Institutes aufbewahrten Typen. - V. Beitrage zur Entomologie, 21 (1 - 2), 79 - 159." type="journal article" year="1971">
Gaedike (
<number box="[410,468,404,428]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" value="1971.0">1971</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
and not studied by 
<bibRefCitation author="Eger" box="[703,832,404,429]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" refString="Eger, J. E. Jr. (1990) Revision of the genus Polytes Stal (Heteroptera: Scutelleridae). Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 83 (2), 115 - 141. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / 83.2.115" type="journal article" year="1990">Eger (1990</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Eger" box="[845,905,404,428]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" refString="Eger, J. E. Jr. (1994) New synonymy in the genus Polytes Stal (Heteroptera, Scutelleridae). Florida Entomologist, 77 (3), 376 - 378. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.2307 / 3496108" type="journal article" year="1994">1994</bibRefCitation>
). The 
<typeStatus box="[977,1073,405,429]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">paratype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[1113,1247,404,428]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="352" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="quechuus">
<emphasis box="[1113,1247,404,428]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. quechuus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
deposited in the 
<collectionCode box="[151,219,440,464]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">DEIC</collectionCode>
, discussed above, perfectly fitting the description of 
<taxonomicName box="[849,998,440,464]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="128" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="speculiger">
<emphasis box="[849,998,440,464]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. speculiger</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
“var. b” and bearing a locality label identical to that of the 
<typeStatus box="[425,531,476,501]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">lectotype</typeStatus>
, is recognized as part of the original 
<typeStatus box="[978,1065,477,501]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">syntype</typeStatus>
series of 
<taxonomicName box="[1186,1335,476,500]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="98" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="speculiger">
<emphasis box="[1186,1335,476,500]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. speculiger</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as well. Although the possibility cannot be excluded, there is no positive indication that this specimen was part of the original 
<typeStatus box="[246,333,549,573]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">syntype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[374,493,548,572]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="372" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="fenestra">
<emphasis box="[374,493,548,572]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. fenestra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, therefore it was probably wrongly recognized as 
<typeStatus box="[1069,1156,549,573]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">syntype</typeStatus>
and wrongly labelled as 
<typeStatus box="[151,302,583,608]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">paralectotype</typeStatus>
of the latter species by 
<bibRefCitation author="Gaedike" box="[576,756,583,608]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" refString="Gaedike, H. (1971) Katalog der in den Sammlungen des ehemaligen Deutschen Entomologischen Institutes aufbewahrten Typen. - V. Beitrage zur Entomologie, 21 (1 - 2), 79 - 159." type="journal article" year="1971">
Gaedike (
<number box="[687,747,584,608]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" value="1971.0">1971</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. The subjective synonymy of 
<emphasis box="[1098,1241,584,608]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. s p e cu l i g er</emphasis>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1301,1435,584,608]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="468" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="quechuus">
<emphasis box="[1301,1435,584,608]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. quechuus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
proposed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Eger" box="[298,434,620,645]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" refString="Eger, J. E. Jr. (1994) New synonymy in the genus Polytes Stal (Heteroptera, Scutelleridae). Florida Entomologist, 77 (3), 376 - 378. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.2307 / 3496108" type="journal article" year="1994">
Eger (
<number box="[367,425,620,644]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" value="1994.0">1994</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
is confirmed now based on the examination of the newly discovered 
<typeStatus box="[1227,1275,621,645]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">type</typeStatus>
material of 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="5" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="speculiger">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. speculiger</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,151,824]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">
<emphasis box="[199,410,692,716]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">
Polytes 
<taxonomicName box="[293,410,692,716]" class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="speculiger">speculiger</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
is readily recognizable based on the pair of unpunctured, yellow lateral patches of the pronotum; 
<bibRefCitation author="Eger" box="[277,414,728,752]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" refString="Eger, J. E. Jr. (1990) Revision of the genus Polytes Stal (Heteroptera: Scutelleridae). Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 83 (2), 115 - 141. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / 83.2.115" type="journal article" year="1990">
Eger (
<number box="[348,406,728,752]" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" value="1990.0">1990</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
provided a detailed description and illustrations of the male genitalia under the name 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Scutelleridae" genus="Pachycoris" genus.bestMatchDistance="531" genus.bestMatchVote="2" genus.innerRound="1" genus.outerRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="557" phylum="Arthropoda" species="quechuus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="557">P. quechuus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
